### Module 4 — REST API + Zod Validation

@base = http://localhost:3000

# ─── LIST ────────────────────────────────────────────────

### GET all posts
GET {{base}}/posts

### With pagination
GET {{base}}/posts?page=1&limit=1

### Filter by published
GET {{base}}/posts?published=true

### Invalid query param (limit must be a number)
GET {{base}}/posts?limit=abc


# ─── READ ────────────────────────────────────────────────

### GET by ID
GET {{base}}/posts/1

### Not found
GET {{base}}/posts/999

### Invalid ID
GET {{base}}/posts/abc


# ─── CREATE ──────────────────────────────────────────────

### Valid post
POST {{base}}/posts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "My New Post",
  "body": "This is the body of my new post, it has enough content.",
  "tags": ["learning", "express"],
  "published": true
}

### Missing required fields → 422 with field-level errors
POST {{base}}/posts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Hi"
}

### Too many tags → 422
POST {{base}}/posts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Tag overload",
  "body": "This post has way too many tags attached to it.",
  "tags": ["a", "b", "c", "d", "e", "f"]
}


# ─── UPDATE ──────────────────────────────────────────────

### PUT (full replacement) — all fields required
PUT {{base}}/posts/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated Title via PUT",
  "body": "This replaces the entire post, all fields required.",
  "tags": ["updated"],
  "published": true
}

### PATCH (partial update) — only send what you want to change
PATCH {{base}}/posts/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "published": true
}


# ─── DELETE ──────────────────────────────────────────────

### Delete a post (returns 204, no body)
DELETE {{base}}/posts/2

### Try to delete it again → 404
DELETE {{base}}/posts/2
